gov.usgs.subspaceprocess

Class FilterCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.subspaceprocess.FilterCollection

  • public final class FilterCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains up to 3 channels of filters. In SubspacePreprocess it is just used to pass the filtering parameters around (hpc, lpc, npoles, type). In the actual SubpaceDectecor real time portion this is used to do the filtering as well.
